column6:
Issue #4 - Issue #5 -
  • The conclusion of Hunting Season!
  • New York City is under biological attack. Can Wolverine save it before it’s too late?
  • Guest starring Nick Fury!
  • “Drowning Logan” starts here!
  • SHIELD agents everywhere, but not a comrade in sight!
  • Wolverine finds himself trapped on a helicarrier – and it’s plunging into the depths of the Atlantic Ocean!
column8: | writer:Paul Cornell | penciler (cover):Alan Davis | inker (cover):Mark Farmer | editor:Jeanine Schaefer
